{"tid":1440612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"颱風利奇馬浙江登陸 永嘉縣堰塞湖即決堤　增至18死仍有14人失蹤","createTime":"2019-08-10T13:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T14:54:40.000Z","uid":54373,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"0ab7e41a12ef6b95bc8f9a806313e4f5f3c7379f","tid":1440612,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:09:44.000Z","msg":"颱風利奇馬凌晨在浙江溫嶺市登陸，永嘉縣岩坦鎮山早村因特大暴雨，引發山泥傾瀉，形成堰塞湖並突然決提，死亡人數增至18人，仍有14人失蹤，當局加緊搜救。浙江全省有超過300萬人受災，200多間房屋倒塌，3000多間房屋受損，多處斷電。利奇馬已減弱為強烈熱帶風暴，上海疏散洋山港、長江上海段1000多艘船隻，郵輪推遲進港。"},{"pid":"75454266d940b412b82b299e27a501f033871640","tid":1440612,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d647eb3eef9aa20ee90e4b89a7ab927e652872","tid":1440612,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4830f8eed2f54ae1461cf84c0611c32f81b7c80b","tid":1440612,"uid":118322,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:10:47.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d669e32b31f6c781cc773a59e04bd98d67bebc4","tid":1440612,"uid":54264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"爽"},{"pid":"7a6ba50823ab46ac1b16460f37f774efd63b221d","tid":1440612,"uid":15943,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:11:30.000Z","msg":"天滅中共<br />\n然後黎手轉頭四川又地震就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc8bad1805f5ed491ac73c214195ed0de667337","tid":1440612,"uid":22360,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:11:34.000Z","msg":"18+14 =32<br />\n<br />\n仲有3個名額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 